Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:05.80,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gouda Takeo, a first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:08.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,The skies are blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.32,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.90,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,The trees and bugs are all doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:13.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:17.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They're clovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:29.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, you look like a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:07.10,Title1,Sign 0204,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,516)}My Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:10.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you today, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I told you it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was a great birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:18.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:24.74,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato and I are having a picnic, \Nas a do-over of her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:24.41,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 0224,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD7B9F0&}ha ha ha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, looks like your backpack's too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:40.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, like bento boxes and a water bottle and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is all from bento boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are snacks, hand towels,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,a picnic blanket,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and trash bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.10,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So much... It must've been tough to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I made too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I got ahead of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you can finish everything, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:01.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.52,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.70,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That pin looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:09.20,SignB,Sign 0307,0000,0000,0000,,2km to Summit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:08.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, it's a really nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:20.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:21.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to take a small break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:27.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:29.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stronger than I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm slow, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this more of a hike than a picnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:40.49,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 0336,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4F5253&}Didn't ask Sunakawa this time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.12,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was having so much fun, I started \Nhumming without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.79,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.29,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:05.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I bet bentos taste great \Nat the top of a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:05.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It gets hot when you walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:17.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:19.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The pin you gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.20,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato's bentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,The crown of flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:00.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I saved the bentos, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we can get \Nback up there by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.63,Phone,Sign 0517,0000,0000,0000,,No Signal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, we don't have a signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:19.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.13,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0522,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(379,1)\c&H7B6F64&}Missing After Going on a Picnic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.01,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0525,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Meanwhile, Yamato's Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.01,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Rinko today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.44,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,She's on a picnic with Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.14,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a picnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.64,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.56,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.47,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,How long have they been dating? Two months?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:38.79,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun was hot,\Nbut I bet he's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.15,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,We could barely talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.85,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.44,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko's boyfriend isn't bad, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.15,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,He's, like, not hot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:53.29,SignC,Sign 0549,0000,0000,0000,,Manly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.79,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Manly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.73,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.29,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Not hot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:57.94,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Seems Rinko thinks he's hotter \Nthan Sunakawa-kun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:58.54,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.17,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.92,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0602,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Meanwhile, at the Gouda household
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:05.29,Default,TDad,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.76,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.80,Default,TDad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.62,Default,TDad,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, where'd Takeo run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.39,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.93,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.15,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he with Makoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:20.05,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.19,Default,TDad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.19,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0623,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Meanwhile, Sunakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:27.03,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 0624,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\an8\fs20}Book 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:31.03,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 0628,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\an8\fs20}Book 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any signs of anyone \Nhaving passed through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:45.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try looking around from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Above?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.72,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd grabbed on to a tree or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.73,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:07.48,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,But no use crying over spilled milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, what I should do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:14.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,is to get Yamato home safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:23.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear cars in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:27.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's a road over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But it's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Reaching the city might take till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:39.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then... We'd have to spend the \Nwhole night by ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:45.98,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 0744,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4FD460&}The whole night by ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:51.49,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, we have to head south.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's south?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow me, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just make progress while the sun's still up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:13.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:19.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We might get separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, you can hang on to my shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, do you want to eat the bentos?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Digging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that good at normal cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Food tastes great outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, was that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave half for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going until night falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.47,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.51,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want to put her at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We can't really see where we're going anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to camp here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep here, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.18,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Camp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.04,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun and me, just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:18.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.42,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them bite Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:28.48,EyecatchA,Sign 1028,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H13282F&}Mosquito
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.98,EyecatchB,Sign 1029,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6EA5CC&}Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.98,EyecatchA,Sign 1030,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\c&HBBBD5C&}Night
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, is your cell still not getting a signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:36.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:37.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:45.58,Phone,Sign 1041,0000,0000,0000,,No Signal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It still says no signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:50.42,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,And if you set your screen to that, \Nyou'll find a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.34,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.47,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Who could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.57,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.97,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rinko's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.97,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.14,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:02.58,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.26,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko hasn't come home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.03,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.27,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want to know if she's with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:10.27,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 1109,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HCA9BF3&}Not Back From a Date
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.56,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 111,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HCA9BF3&}Not Back From a Date = Overnight Stay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.14,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:16.09,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko's with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.19,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We have other friends with us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.19,SignD,Sign 1118,0000,0000,0000,,The Lies Borne of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.63,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.51,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,You want to talk to her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.73,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but she's taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:23.54,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.68,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.53,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.29,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:29.52,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're all going to stay over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.24,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.71,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:36.59,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.39,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Calling Rinko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:37.97,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Calling now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.09,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Telling her we gave her an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.52,Default,Ph,0000,0000,0000,,You're being redirected to voicemail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:42.93,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.02,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through to her cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.09,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.06,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.34,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.04,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Sunakawa-kun'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.82,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone have his number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:55.48,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.61,Kurihara,Sign 1156,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.24,Default,Kurihara,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.11,Default,Kurihara,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.66,Default,Kurihara,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your calling me \Nduring the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.58,Default,Kurihara,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing going on tomorrow—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:08.54,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know where Rinko and her \Nboyfriend went after their picnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.99,Default,Kurihara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A picnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:10.88,Default,Kurihara,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:11.85,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:12.61,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.21,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1215,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Meanwhile, at the Goudas
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.59,Default,TDad,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, how are you feeling—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.27,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:23.09,Default,TDad,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo's still not back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.03,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.82,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:27.62,Default,TDad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.30,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.86,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him eat it for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.23,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put plastic wrap on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.23,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1233,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Meanwhile, Sunakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:39.23,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 1235,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\an8\fs20}Book 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,At night, it's pitch dark in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takeo-kun, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:12:59.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She must be worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is something coming at us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it was just a boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A boa—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.51,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato sounds worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.01,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:49.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight off anything, even a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.60,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:55.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Moon's out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.77,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If it's this bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.82,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato won't be as worried anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.11,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:11.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired from walking all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:15.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.21,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:25.14,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We're lying next to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:25.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:26.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can see a lot because it's really dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:40.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's like being at the planetarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.60,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a happy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:50.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You always ask if I'm all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:02.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.83,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:14.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind if we had to stay out \Nhere for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'd still be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.08,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seeing Takeo-kun asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're all worn out because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And here I am with my head in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I like you a lot, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:00.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.81,SFX-Red,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch Scratch Scratch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.70,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.64,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seeing her asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all the critters around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When you're around Takeo-kun, you feel safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:28.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.03,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The road!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:51.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:51.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.74,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect her from everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've got a lot of bites!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:02.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been popular with mosquitoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:07.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I managed to attract one,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I saved you from one bite, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.32,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.78,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I should call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:25.04,Phone,Sign 1822,0000,0000,0000,,New Message from Nanako \N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:22.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have a text from Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.63,Message Body - Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:34.05,Phone,Sign 1826,0000,0000,0000,,To: Yamato Rinko \NSubject: Rinko~~!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.68,Message Body - Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I smoothed things over with your fam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.41,Message Body - Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come over tomorrow \Nand tell us everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:32.79,Message Body - Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be here waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.01,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go to Nanako's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, tell her hi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've spent so much time together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,leaving you feels kind of lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.92,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.42,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 1918,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\an8}Incoming Call \NKurihara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.52,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.01,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.85,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I couldn't get what you told me \Nyesterday out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.19,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between \NTakeo and Rinko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.43,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.37,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here's Rinko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.52,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.52,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,We even pulled an all-nighter waiting for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.05,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:36.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:41.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I thought I'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.66,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1943,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HACA6D4&}Fun Last Night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.66,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god! Perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.17,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:46.51,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that sensitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.31,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.29,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,So, details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:53.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was so nervous, \NI thought my heart would burst...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was my first time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We were outside the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:19:59.92,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,What? Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But Takeo-kun made me feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A boar showed up, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I slept just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:10.34,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.15,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're all muddy, Rinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.44,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.52,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 2015,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\an8}Incoming Call \NKurihara
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We kind of got lost in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:16.69,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:22.45,Gouda,Sign 2018,0000,0000,0000,,Gouda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.11,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.45,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.18,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:24.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.65,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Mountains, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:27.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Were you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:28.79,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.12,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 2035,0000,0000,0000,,Received Message
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.46,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 2035,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato Rinko \NSubject: Glad We're OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:35.46,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we got back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.45,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You had to work really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.57,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry my head was in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:45.11,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was excited and nervous that I got \Nto spend a lot of time with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.51,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.72,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.67,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 2100,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\an8\fs20}...was still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.56,Default,Sign 2100,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me about emoticons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't express my feelings for Yamato in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... What kind of feelings would they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:11.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Whomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Dazzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:22.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wham, shazam, kabloom, and fwoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:23.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Blam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, I don't think emoticons will help you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:24.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wham!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:27.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Dazzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kabloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Dun dun dun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.97,Phone,Sign 2130,0000,0000,0000,,Received Message \NFrom: Takeo-kun \NTo: Yamato Rinko \NSubject: RE: Glad We're OK \NMe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:35.37,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:51.01,Title2,Sign 2247,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,515)}My Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:49.25,Default - margin,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: My Ocean.
